            <fr:title text="Examples of regular expression matching">Examples of regular expression matching</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>Consider <fr:link href="jms-017D.xml" title="The matching relation for regular expressions" addr="jms-017D" type="local">regular expression matching</fr:link> over the alphabet <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Sigma ={\mathopen {}\left \{a,b\right \}\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
            <fr:ol><fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\vert  b]]></fr:tex> is matched by each symbol in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Sigma ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li>
 <fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(a\vert  b)*]]></fr:tex> is matched every <fr:link href="jms-016I.xml" title="String over an alphabet" addr="jms-016I" type="local">string</fr:link> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Sigma ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li>
 <fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b(a\vert  b)*]]></fr:tex> is matched by any <fr:link href="jms-016I.xml" title="String over an alphabet" addr="jms-016I" type="local">string</fr:link> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Sigma ]]></fr:tex> that starts with a <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li>
 <fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[((a\vert  b)(a\vert  b))*]]></fr:tex> is matched by any <fr:link href="jms-016I.xml" title="String over an alphabet" addr="jms-016I" type="local">string</fr:link> of even length over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Sigma ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li>
 <fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(\underline {\epsilon }\vert  a)(\underline {\epsilon }\vert  b)\vert  bb]]></fr:tex> is matched just by the <fr:link href="jms-016I.xml" title="String over an alphabet" addr="jms-016I" type="local">strings</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\epsilon ]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[ab]]></fr:tex>, and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[bb]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li>
 <fr:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\varnothing  b\vert  a]]></fr:tex> is matched only by the symbol <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li></fr:ol>
          </fr:mainmatter>
